Initial commit
Add New Relic support to WSGI file.
Update vendor to use HTTPS product-details url.
Change vendor submodule URL to HTTPS.

Start migration numbers at 001, not 000.

The way schematic determines what migration a database is on causes it
to think it's on version 0 if it's never run a migration, meaning that
it skips over migration 000. So the first migration has to be 001 in
order to be run.
Remove extra migration.
Remove preview field from migration 000; it's added in 001.
